@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #0F172A
  LifeLineBorderColor #334155
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  ParticipantBorderColor #334155
}

title Sequence - Xem lịch sử đặt vé

actor Customer as "Khách hàng"
participant UI as "[[../../client/src/features/user/pages/ProfileInfoPage.tsx TicketHistoryPage]]"
participant Hook as "[[../../client/src/features/booking/hooks/useMyBookings.ts useMyBookings]]"
participant API as "[[../../client/src/lib/api-client.ts apiClient]]"
control Ctl as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/controller/booking/BookingController.java BookingController]]"
participant Svc as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/service/BookingService.java BookingService]]"
database Repo as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/repo/BookingRepository.java BookingRepository]]"

== Tải lịch sử đặt vé ==
Customer -> UI: Truy cập trang lịch sử vé
UI -> Hook: [[../../client/src/features/booking/hooks/useMyBookings.ts useMyBookings(page, limit)]]
Hook -> API: [[../../client/src/features/booking/services/booking.service.ts getMyBookingApi({ page, limit })]] GET /api/bookings/me?page&size
API -> Ctl: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/controller/booking/BookingController.java#L50 getMyBookings(currentUser, page, size)]]
Ctl -> Svc: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/service/BookingService.java getBookingHistory(userId, pageable)]]
Svc -> Repo: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/repo/BookingRepository.java findByUserIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(...)]]
Repo --> Svc: Page<Booking>
Svc --> Ctl: Page<BookingResponse>
Ctl --> API: 200 OK
API --> Hook: Dữ liệu phân trang
Hook --> UI: Render danh sách giao dịch
UI --> Customer: Hiển thị thông tin vé, ghế, tổng tiền, trạng thái
@enduml
